metadata.name: It Came From Outer Space! #0/10
metadata.description:
This is Token 0 or the "Genesis" of the The Starcrossed Series One

She kept running. 
She didn't know what this distortion of reality that had suddenly appeared days ago but she was afraid of it.  YOU NEED TO GET OUT OF HERE! A mans voice called out, She stopped moving as went to respond but before she did, a beam of light illuminated the man, ARRRRAHHG!. A terrifying scream was the only thing she could hear. The man as he was yelling, started to hover in the air as his body was seemingly ripped apart from reality. Her watch like gauntlet chimed rapidly with warnings noises. It was just like like the others she saw before. She knew that she had to keep moving, but she was well aware she was running out of energy even as adrenaline filled her system, she knew didnâ€™t want to be taken like the rest of them. 

And so, she kept running...
